{"tid":2266900,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都覺得所有身邊嘅朋友都會講自己壞話","createTime":"2020-11-01T16:12:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T17:51:59.000Z","uid":311743,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6d15ac84ad690322b357b668b2522c073deb387e","tid":2266900,"uid":311743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:12:16.000Z","msg":"自小社交圈子都好細<br />\n明明都覺得自己好就得人 好為人切想<br />\n朋友有咩事 都兩脇插刀 義不容辭 幫到底果隻<br />\n但成日都俾人當係傻仔 當係屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得唯一果一兩個好朋友 <br />\n都會係其他人面對講自己壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n覺得其實佢哋根本就唔鐘意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n人多疑真係好煩，識朋友仲煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0e0adcfdff0ff6af7cb41b0e8048b977ed4696","tid":2266900,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有1-2個交心，好過有1堆酒肉朋友"},{"pid":"0b3320ff685453b982d3d2db4ff22df40ed31ee7","tid":2266900,"uid":359504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"咁佢地鬧你咩先"},{"pid":"e4fb193495f5fbfa3dea4b36b5fa14b3669d5c4e","tid":2266900,"uid":311743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b3320ff685453b982d3d2db4ff22df40ed31ee7","tid":2266900,"uid":359504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"咁佢地鬧你咩先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:17:49.000Z","msg":"純粹覺得所以朋友都對住自己人前人後，唔知佢哋鬧咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1cd98b201e622fa38c9e246b0ec33773566f79","tid":2266900,"uid":311743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"1a0e0adcfdff0ff6af7cb41b0e8048b977ed4696","tid":2266900,"uid":301809,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-01T16:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\